From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Entrpi <entrpi@proton.me>
Date: Mon, 16 Feb 2026 17:46:33 +1100
Subject: [PATCH] thermal: cix: Add Sky1 thermal, power domain, and cpufreq
 support

Add CIX thermal zone driver, IPA power integration for
cpufreq_cooling, pmdomain ACPI genpd provider for SCMI
power and perf domains, and cpufreq CPPC fixes.
---
